high_descs: Turn left then take a step to your left.
Pick up the black plate that's in front of you on the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn right and walk to the sink then turn right and walk to the fridge.
Chill the plate in the fridge then take it back out and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the stove that's in front of you to the left.
Put the plate in the microwave then close the door.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and step forward, then turn right to face the stove.
Pick up the plate from the counter to the left of the stove.
Turn right and move forward, then turn right to go to the fridge.
Open the fridge, put the plate inside and chill it, then take the plate out.
Turn around and return to the stove, then look up at the microwave above it.
Open the microwave, put the plate inside, then close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a cold plate in the microwave.

turn around to the right go right towards the refrigerator
put the plate inside the refrigerator get it back out
turn to the right go right towards the microwave
put the plate inside the microwave
